show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/wMXBcn
show.description: A woman is falsely accused of causing the death of her brother-in-law's child. Based on baseless suspicions, her husband believes the misunderstanding and, in a fit of rage, forces her out of the house and demands a divorce. This puts their love, trust, and unity through a severe test.
